<br>
Only one thing ya missed with respect to manaburn's downside... it really limits VI's options for future encounters.  Since it's not resistable, there simply can't be any worthwhile single group encounter mobs that have less than about 6x average manaburn hp, or the encounter is probably trivial before it's even introduced.  Same deal with raid mobs, only on a bigger scale.<br>
