oh well, the game is Evercaster now anyway (and monks with insane AC thanks to ridiculously high AC monk items in north ToV and beyond... and don't get me started on the AC softcap)).  Put an epic mage in your group and watch that pet go.  It was already sick.  A mage friend with his epic agreed with me on that before.  then recently they made it even better for no apparent reason at all.  &quot;Hey, it's really powerful!  Let's make it hit more accurately and give it better saves so it will be even more uber!&quot;  <br>
