-- Callon <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/usolinarinnoruuk.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Solinar Innoruuk</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>is a Formidable Opponent</span><br>  Posts: 144<br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/29/02 2:49:16 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1790.topic&index=90>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Team Manaburn...blessing or Curse?</span><hr size=1> AoW has a million HP, and cannot be slowed, while Kerafym is slowable.<br>
